{"id":"c4fd18cb6babd6f6149fc154e03b95fbe3efba0b82db824baf6f36eb91ad9abb","text":"将颜色的各个独立通道钳制在指定的最小值和最大值之间。如果某个 RGB 通道值小于最小值，就会被设为最小值；如果某个 RGB 通道大于最大值，就会被设为最大值。"}
{"id":"35aea6f833e7d09d9722a54bdee4bc25b02fd25547d6613ee8d9457096af94fb","text":"Input Color"}
{"id":"e20b5bcd5e763d430c9a1d69a4eef0297680ac2211959ec9e40e62b62e491287","text":"此颜色的 R、G、B 各通道都会被钳制在指定的最小值和最大值之间。例如，如果颜色值为"}
{"id":"f38d1558b39ea5cb156ad74a2bec94d64b7a6fe6d75f1baca423f15a0287f235","text":"，并指定最小值为"}
{"id":"4caf7207558746dbf4b3c4fab7494df042edcd792ee8f159bd95493e5c057675","text":"、最大值为"}
{"id":"a81653c14511570a6dff803f596cb87b83c23e82f58d7e5ae2378276a3be380a","text":"，则得到的颜色将为"}
{"item_id":"9e5afc67d0:7","text":"。"}
{"id":"dea79332147ffe1fb2a81cf9a5bdf0066ddcc625699996ede0ce140e5cb004b1","text":"Min"}
{"id":"2730b48ee4a343b2e74d7132f1486ffe327669ed494fa18c2794be0e9b6fd6fa","text":"每个颜色通道允许的最小值。"}
{"id":"a1a5936d3b0f8a69fd62c91ed9990d3bd414c5e78c603e2837c65c9f46a93eb8","text":"Max"}
{"id":"e2541f5d231811c1c3b15eb7527c4215e269c675cb53458a348357657549ccfa","text":"每个颜色通道允许的最大值。"}
{"id":"8b76e2df9050f924b018cff8809cbc580f39a71664984ae54adf99defe9eaa2e","text":"Output Parameters"}
{"id":"d76cd2ea3537dbac1a9b90ba977fe5ad654d6f7f3c36b060963224d8b5611f99","text":"resultRGB"}
{"id":"6796d2c52b4882b98311c8be5b2889976246b071d35733a80a01da19e5bcba42","text":"钳制后的颜色结果。"}
